title: Am I the Jerk - Cancelling Small Wedding Last Minute
description: Sydney wrote to the show explaining how her & her fiance planned a small wedding lasting no longer than 2 hour a while back, and are both getting cold feet last minute. Are they the jerks for wanting to cancel?
